AttributeList.Text:
How to control and set the IR lamp: To turn on the IR lamp the machine needs to be started and the doors closed. Heater setpoint should be set from 0-100 "Heater_Setpoint", lamp should be turned on by "Heater_ON_OFF". The lamp will activate only when the certain conditions are meet (position/direction/time).
Right now, the signal from NOAH is being send when spreading and the permission for the lamp is being keep in the function block for a certain period of time to enable the lamp on the way back.
E-STOP - always check!
Modes: 0 - Heating Feedbox/Printbox when spreading and executing the heater on the way back from PLC 1 - Heating only on the way back from NOAH
Safety is based only on timer. Hardware protection should be implemented ASAP (contactor controlled by thermal fuse / thermistor to cut off the power if the temperature exceeds certain level).
Things to implement: - Remote temperature sensor(already purchased some time ago). - Heater_MathFunction to operate heater better based on the measured results - PID control
